  description: "pathlib.PurePath.match.__name__ == 'match' — match() tests a path against a glob pattern; 'match' has 5 characters; match (5) is the minimum length in the covered set; confirmed Python 3.14.3 macOS"
  category: identity
  kind: python_call_eq
  function: PurePath.match.__name__.__eq__
  args: ["match"]
  expected: true

