  description: "pathlib.PurePath.match.__name__.__len__() == 5 — 'match' has 5 characters; match (5) < joinpath (8): the two shortest covered names differ by 3; match (5) is the minimum length; confirmed Python 3.14.3 macOS"
  category: identity
  kind: python_call_eq
  function: PurePath.match.__name__.__len__
  args: []
  expected: 5

